":187493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:03:49.000Z","msg":"你班人知藝術家係咩呀？Juno咪係囉，你越睇唔明就代表佢越有藝術細胞同時代表你做唔到藝術家呀。<br />\n佢個畫面一係就有幾光就幾光同有幾暗就要幾暗，表現光同暗既分別。鏡頭係亂咁插無關係既Montage，代表佢對社會混亂既控訴呀。<br />\n你班人睇唔唔睇得明法國導演大師Jean-Luc Godard啲戲呀？<br />\nJuno佢而家已經做到咁既境界，Juno簡直係港版Jean-Luc Godard呀，香港新浪潮既先行者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：其實我都睇唔明佢做緊乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526739e46be7f1fd73468cf3ebee7ec6d44f7d71","tid":1158310,"uid":121450,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/XBKNFnJFdplDOzfwP0/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FXBKNFnJFdplDOzfwP0%2Fgiphy.gif&h=d036e0fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d097062157e166d0119b266429fd791079a148b","tid":1158310,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:39:49.000Z","msg":"鬼片嚟？"},{"pid":"17a35125bc8191c8f5e7b87cbe734f89f0e7c5aa","tid":1158310,"uid":121450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g6o6jYs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg6o6jYs.png&h=c65d2c1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a00410cc2d66284f926d082dfbf29d673692e69f","tid":1158310,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38a952e35d3ab1b3c571949606c66cb1ed5bc7db","tid":1158310,"uid":156652,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:52:58.000Z","msg":"拍九唔搭八畫面，講幾句扮有深度句子，我屌你啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:38:12.000Z","msg":"國王的新衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77270cc27ad881b6ee72f8523e6aece2d2a39118","tid":1158310,"uid":121450,"like":1,"d